          "p_description"
        ],
        "notes_should_not_contain": "No Smart Properties bindings detected"
      }
    },
    {
      "_case": "link-field-dead-end",
      "_desc": "Module with a top-level `link` field in esd-dynamic-block AND no proper CTA variable bindings in the variables array. This is the OG-preview dead-end case the probe documented \u2014 the wizard emits a top-level link when it crawls an anchor target, but the API silently ignores it at compose time. The anchor carries es-button so P2's button-presence gate fires correctly.",
