    {
      "_case": "naming-mismatch-with-orphans",
      "_desc": "Mirrors the live module 1653410 from production: Smart Properties registered with names that do NOT match their bound class basename (p_title bound to .esd-gen-title, not .esd-gen-p-title), AND a top-level link field, AND additional orphan esd-gen-* classes on the button that have no matching registered variable. The anchor carries es-button so P2's button-presence gate fires and the CTA dead-end note fires correctly. This is the canary case for the 0.19.4 fix \u2014 under the old inferred-name cross-reference, ALL esd-gen classes (including the two properly bound ones) were flagged as unmapped. With the selector-based cross-reference, only the three orphan classes should be flagged.",
      "id": 1653411,
      "uid": "jkl-uid-1653411",
      "name": "Text + body + CTA",
      "markup": "<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td class=\"esd-structure\" style=\"padding:20px\"><div esd-dynamic-block=\"{&quot;variables&quot;:[{&quot;variable&quot;:&quot;p_title&quot;,&quot;defaultValue&quot;:&quot;Default Title&quot;,&quot;blockMapping&quot;:[{&quot;selector&quot;:&quot;.esd-gen-title&quot;,&quot;attribute&quot;:&quot;&quot;}]},{&quot;variable&quot;:&quot;p_description&quot;,&quot;defaultValue&quot;:&quot;Default description.&quot;,&quot;blockMapping&quot;:[{&quot;selector&quot;:&quot;.esd-gen-description&quot;,&quot;attribute&quot;:&quot;&quot;}]}],&quot;link&quot;:{&quot;blockMapping&quot;:[{&quot;selector&quot;:&quot;a.esd-gen-Link&quot;,&quot;attribute&quot;:&quot;href&quot;}]}}\"><h1 class=\"esd-gen-title\">Default Title</h1><p class=\"esd-gen-description\">Default description.</p><a class=\"es-button esd-gen-Link esd-gen-p-link\" href=\"https://example.com\"><span class=\"esd-gen-p-cta-text\">Click</span></a></div></td></tr></table>",
      "css": "",
      "_expected": {
        "registered_variables": [
          {
            "name": "p_title",
            "blockMapping": [
              {
                "selector": ".esd-gen-title",
                "attribute": ""
              }
