    {
      "_case": "static-asset-alt-title-padding",
      "_desc": "P1 regression: 1 variable with src as its PRIMARY binding (p_image) and 3 variables whose PRIMARY binding is innerText but carry secondary alt/title mappings on the same image selector. Under the old multi-condition predicate, p_title/p_caption/p_label would each be counted as image-bound (via p_image* name prefix or alt/title attribute), pushing the count to 4 and falsely firing the static-asset note. With the isImageSrcPrimary predicate, only p_image qualifies \u2014 count is 1, below threshold, no note.",
      "id": 9010,
      "uid": "aaa-uid-9010",
      "name": "Hero \u2014 alt/title padding false positive check",
      "markup": "<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td class=\"esd-structure\" style=\"padding:20px\"><div esd-dynamic-block=\"{&quot;variables&quot;:[{&quot;variable&quot;:&quot;p_image&quot;,&quot;defaultValue&quot;:&quot;https://example.com/tick.png&quot;,&quot;blockMapping&quot;:[{&quot;selector&quot;:&quot;.esd-gen-image&quot;,&quot;attribute&quot;:&quot;src&quot;}]},{&quot;variable&quot;:&quot;p_title&quot;,&quot;defaultValue&quot;:&quot;Title&quot;,&quot;blockMapping&quot;:[{&quot;selector&quot;:&quot;.esd-gen-title&quot;,&quot;attribute&quot;:&quot;&quot;},{&quot;selector&quot;:&quot;.esd-gen-image&quot;,&quot;attribute&quot;:&quot;alt&quot;}]},{&quot;variable&quot;:&quot;p_caption&quot;,&quot;defaultValue&quot;:&quot;Caption&quot;,&quot;blockMapping&quot;:[{&quot;selector&quot;:&quot;.esd-gen-caption&quot;,&quot;attribute&quot;:&quot;&quot;},{&quot;selector&quot;:&quot;.esd-gen-image&quot;,&quot;attribute&quot;:&quot;title&quot;}]},{&quot;variable&quot;:&quot;p_label&quot;,&quot;defaultValue&quot;:&quot;Label&quot;,&quot;blockMapping&quot;:[{&quot;selector&quot;:&quot;.esd-gen-label&quot;,&quot;attribute&quot;:&quot;&quot;},{&quot;selector&quot;:&quot;.esd-gen-image&quot;,&quot;attribute&quot;:&quot;alt&quot;}]}]}\"><img class=\"esd-gen-image\" src=\"https://example.com/tick.png\" alt=\"Title\" /><h1 class=\"esd-gen-title\">Title</h1><p class=\"esd-gen-caption\">Caption</p><span class=\"esd-gen-label\">Label</span></div></td></tr></table>",
