      "_case": "selector-without-target-ack-attr",
      "_desc": "P3: p_title has selector .esd-gen-title (present in HTML) and a second blockMapping for .esd-gen-missing-title (absent). p_image has .esd-gen-image absent. An ACK marker for p_image.src suppresses only the p_image note. p_title's selector-without-target note should still fire (no ACK for it) \u2014 wait, actually p_title's first selector .esd-gen-title IS present so only the second mapping fires. But note: the current selector-without-target check only fires for .esd-gen-* selectors, and only once per missing selector. In this fixture we test that the ACK suppresses the specific (p_image, src) pair.",
